9: ## Requirements\\n350: \\n351: ### Feature: CleanupManager Resource...\n  Line 55: {\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1775881187485,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2853ed3b7ffekZ0flphk6ou8DL\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ac460e00018ElBi9SpH3JXZR\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ac452950014A5668CSz3bcGj\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2853ed3b7ffekZ0flphk6ou8DL\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Done. I've added the AR-038 delta-spec.md section for Go unit testing in the workloadmanager module. The file now contains:\\n\\n1. **AR-020** (existing): CLI pack command\\n2. **AR-038** (new): Go unit tests for pkg/workloadmanager\\n\\nKey coverage areas in AR-038:\\n- CleanupManager (cleanup.go) - **Missing tests**\\n- BatchManager (batch.go) - **Missing tests** \\n- WorkloadManager sandbox operations (service.go)\\n- Server HTTP handlers (server.go)\\n- GracefulManager (graceful.go)\\n- K8sClient initialization (client.go)\\n- Helper functions (types.go)\\n- ListExpiredSandboxes (gc.go)\\n- Retry logic (retry.go) - **Missing tests**\\n\\nTest file status shows: 3 test files need to be created (cleanup_test.go, batch_test.go, retry_test.go), while existing tests for service, gc, expiration, server, graceful, and client are complete.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775881187483,\"end\":1775881187483}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z_logs/AR-035_ST-4.log:\n  Line 27: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775880972996,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2854178afffe40mg2XimqIneGs\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ac12639001mljVnn8G7CXLxx\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ac11ec3001X2S0tVpT9UaTCA\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2854178afffe40mg2XimqIneGs\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_ccc12f8a76cc4f7d8ff17806\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/design.md\"},\"output\":\"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/design.md</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: # AR-035: client-go 类型客户端生成 — Design/设计说明\\n2: \\n3: ## 1. 架构 (Architecture)\\n4: \\n5: ### 1.1 定位 (Purpose/Positioning)\\n6: \\n7: 本变更将 AgentCube 现有的手写 `client-go` 库替换为由 `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 自动生成的标准 Kubernetes 风格客户端库。当前手写实现中，`real.go` 的 `NewForConfig` 返回空 `Clientset{}`，Informer 使用空的 `ListWatch{}`，Lister 虽然实现了基于 `cache.Indexer` 的查询但缺少与 Informer 的联动。这些 stub 实现无法在真实 Kubernetes 集群中工作。\\n8: \\n9: 生成后的客户端库将为 `AgentRuntime` 和 `CodeInterpreter` CRD（API Group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`）提供：\\n10: 1. **类型安全的 REST 客户端** — 通过 `rest.RESTClient` 与 Kubernetes API Server 通信，支持完整 CRUD + Watch + Patch + DeleteCollection\\n11: 2. **SharedInformerFactory** — 事件驱动的缓存同步机制，支持 `Start`/`Shutdown`/`WaitForCacheSync` 生命周期和 `WithNamespace`/`WithTweakListOptions` 等选项\\n12: 3. **Listers** — 基于 `cache.Indexer` 的只读缓存索引，提供 O(1) 按 key 查询和 O(n) 按 selector 遍历\\n13: 4. **Fake Clientset** — 内存级测试替身，使用 `k8s.io/client-go/testing.Fake` 框架，支持 Action/Reactor 模式\\n14: \\n15: 所有代码由 `make gen-client` → `hack/update-codegen.sh` 自动生成，不应手动修改（`Expansion` 接口除外）。\\n16: \\n17: ### 1.2 目录结构 (Directory Layout)\\n18: \\n19: **当前状态 (Before):**\\n20: \\n21: ```\\n22: client-go/\\n23: ├── clientset/\\n24: │   ├── clientset.go              # Interface (仅 RuntimeV1alpha1(), 无 Discovery())\\n25: │   ├── real.go                   # Clientset (stub: NewForConfig 返回空 Clientset{})\\n26: │   ├── fake.go       ...\n  Line 47: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775880999529,\"sessionID\":\"ses_2854178afffe40mg2XimqIneGs\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7ac18e71001ihrJQl0iJB9Nhz\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7ac18402001Vap2thPt4wIl7u\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_2854178afffe40mg2XimqIneGs\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_efcecf7eb82e4eefbc082bec\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/Makefile\"},\"output\":