ger RBAC** (`templates/rbac/workloadmanager.yaml`)\\n   - ServiceAccount: `workloadmanager`\\n   - ClusterRole: `workloadmanager` (完整的 Sandbox/CodeInterpreter/AgentRuntime 权限)\\n   - ClusterRoleBinding: 绑定 SA 到 ClusterRole\\n\\n2. **Router RBAC** (`templates/rbac-router.yaml`)\\n   - ServiceAccount: `agentcube-router`\\n   - Role: namespace-scoped, Secrets 读写权限\\n   - RoleBinding: 绑定 SA 到 Role\\n   - 支持 `.Values.router.rbac.create` 条件开关\\n\\n3. **测试覆盖**\\n   - `tests/workloadmanager-rbac_test.yaml` - WorkloadManager RBAC 测试\\n   - `tests/rbac-router_test.yaml` - Router RBAC 测试 (8 个测试场景)\\n\\n---\\n\\n### ⏸️ Deferred (已延期)\\n\\n**独立 RBAC Manifest 目录结构** (delta-spec.md 中定义):\\n- `manifests/rbac/namespace.yaml` - Namespace 清单\\n- `manifests/rbac/serviceaccounts/*.yaml` - 独立 SA 文件\\n- `manifests/rbac/clusterroles/*.yaml` - 独立 ClusterRole 文件\\n- `manifests/rbac/clusterrolebindings/*.yaml` - 独立 ClusterRoleBinding 文件\\n- `manifests/rbac/roles/router.yaml` - 独立 Router Role\\n- `manifests/rbac/rolebindings/router.yaml` - 独立 Router RoleBinding\\n- `manifests/rbac/rbac.yaml` - 组合清单\\n- `manifests/rbac/rbac-cleanup.yaml` - 清理清单\\n- `manifests/rbac/validate-rbac.sh` - 验证脚本\\n- `manifests/rbac/README.md` - 使用文档\\n\\n**Volcano Scheduler RBAC** - 未找到独立的 SA/ClusterRole/ClusterRoleBinding 文件\\n\\n**Open Questions 未决议:**\\n1. 是否支持通过 overlay 文件进行细粒度权限定制\\n2. 验证脚本是否集成 CI/CD\\n3. 是否需要 PodSecurityPolicy/PodSecurityStandard 绑定\\n4. 是否需要分级 RBAC profile (minimal/standard/full)\",\"time\":{\"start\":1775881138324,\"end\":1775881138324}}}\n\n/home/dsj/benchmark/results/runs/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-qwen3.5-plus_20260410T163217Z_logs/AR-031_ST-6.log:\n  Line 4: {\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1775880963431,\"sessionID\":\"ses_28540a122ffeV6GyViz90QWuux\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_d7abf6b5f0013OCfvYMQmS9b1p\",\"messageID\":\"msg_d7abf5fd2001n9x3Y2yi0Z5jOC\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_28540a122ffeV6GyViz90QWuux\",\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"task\",\"callID\":\"toolu_f9cfa44bfa82430eae702