{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881471526,"sessionID":"ses_28538c162ffeTvSu32nXKbaKjD","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac85a5c001BwR3pVhm9D9x1h","messageID":"msg_d7ac83a94001anXKtM4JivEYhE","sessionID":"ses_28538c162ffeTvSu32nXKbaKjD","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_93b9016e13a249e8adf5a93d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-038: Go Unit Tests (workloadmanager) - Tasks\n\n> **Module:** pkg/workloadmanager\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** L\n> **Status:** ST-3 Completed\n\n---\n\n## Overview\n\nThis tasks.md defines atomic, independently verifiable tasks for implementing comprehensive Go unit tests for the workloadmanager module. Stage ST-3 (Design) is complete.\n\n---\n\n## Test File Status\n\n| Source File | Test File | Status |\n|-------------|-----------|--------|\n| `service.go` | `service_test.go` | ✅ EXISTS |\n| `client.go` | `client_test.go` | ✅ EXISTS |\n| `gc.go` | `gc_test.go` | ✅ EXISTS |\n| `expiration.go` | `expiration_test.go` | ✅ EXISTS |\n| `graceful.go` | `graceful_test.go` | ✅ EXISTS |\n| `server.go` | `server_test.go` | ✅ EXISTS |\n| `delete_test.go` | `delete_test.go` | ✅ EXISTS |\n| `cleanup.go` | `cleanup_test.go` | 🔲 **MISSING** |\n| `batch.go` | `batch_test.go` | 🔲 **MISSING** |\n| `retry.go` | `retry_test.go` | 🔲 **MISSING** |\n| `events.go` | `events_test.go` | 🔲 **MISSING** |\n| `reconciler/reconciler.go` | `reconciler/reconciler_test.go` | ✅ EXISTS |\n\n---\n\n## Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: CleanupManager Tests (cleanup_test.go)\n\n- [ ] **T-101** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/cleanup_test.go`\n- [ ] **T-102** Implement AR-038-001-A: `cleanupServices` - deletes orphaned services by owner reference\n- [ ] **T-103** Implement AR-038-001-B: `cleanupConfigMaps` - deletes configmaps with auto-delete annotation\n- [ ] **T-104** Implement AR-038-001-C: `cleanupPVCs` - handles Retain policy PVCs correctly\n- [ ] **T-105** Implement AR-038-001-D: `cleanupOrphanedResources` - cleans services, configmaps, PVCs\n- [ ] **T-106** Implement AR-038-001-E: `FindOrphanedServices` - finds services with no owner references\n- [ ] **T-107** Implement AR-038-001-F: `CleanupAllResources` - cleans all associated resources\n- [ ] **T-108** Add edge case tests: empty namespace, API errors, partial failures\n- [ ] **T-109** Verify: All cleanup scenarios pass with fake Kubernetes client\n\n### Phase 2: BatchManager Tests (batch_test.go)\n\n- [ ] **T-201** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/batch_test.go`\n- [ ] **T-202** Implement AR-038-002-A: `handleDeleteAllSandboxes` synchronous (≤10 items)\n- [ ] **T-203** Implement AR-038-002-B: `handleDeleteAllSandboxes` async (>10 items)\n- [ ] **T-204** Implement AR-038-002-C: `handleDeleteByLabelSelector` with label filtering\n- [ ] **T-205** Implement AR-038-002-D: `deleteStaleSandboxes` concurrent deletion handling\n- [ ] **T-206** Implement AR-038-002-E: BatchManager handles empty results\n- [ ] **T-207** Add edge case tests: all deletions fail, partial failures, context cancellation\n- [ ] **T-208** Verify: All batch scenarios pass with mock WorkloadManager\n\n### Phase 3: Retry Logic Tests (retry_test.go)\n\n- [ ] **T-301** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/retry_test.go`\n- [ ] **T-302** Test `retryDeletion` succeeds on first attempt\n- [ ] **T-303** Test `retryDeletion` succeeds after retry\n- [ ] **T-304** Test `retryDeletion` fails after max retries\n- [ ] **T-305** Test `retryDeletion` respects context cancellation\n- [ ] **T-306** Test exponential backoff behavior\n- [ ] **T-307** Test backoff ceiling (max 5 seconds)\n- [ ] **T-308** Verify: Retry logic handles all error scenarios correctly\n\n### Phase 4: EventRecorder Tests (events_test.go)\n\n- [ ] **T-401** Create `pkg/workloadmanager/events_test.go`\n- [ ] **T-402** Test `emitDeletionEvent` creates valid Event objects\n- [ ] **T-403** Test event contains correct sandbox metadata\n- [ ] **T-404** Test event reason and message formatting\n- [ ] **T-405** Test EventRecorder handles API server errors gracefully\n- [ ] **T-406** Verify: Events emitted correctly with fake Kubernetes client\n\n### Phase 5: Integration & Coverage Verification\n\n- [ ] **T-501** Run all unit tests: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v`\n- [ ] **T-502** Generate coverage report: `go test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -coverprofile=coverage.out`\n- [ ] **T-503** Verify coverage ≥ 70% target\n- [ ] **T-504** Add any missing edge case coverage identified in report\n- [ ] **T-505** Run `go vet ./pkg/workloadmanager/...`\n- [ ] **T-506** Run `gofmt -s` on all test files\n\n---\n\n## Test Execution Commands\n\n```bash\n# Run all tests\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -v\n\n# Run with coverage\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -coverprofile=coverage.out -covermode=atomic\n\n# View coverage report\ngo tool cover -html=coverage.out -o coverage.html\n\n# Run specific test file\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/cleanup_test.go -v\n\n# Run tests matching pattern\ngo test ./pkg/workloadmanager/... -run \"TestCleanup\" -v\n```\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n- Go 1.21+\n- `testing` package (stdlib)\n- `k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes/fake` for Kubernetes client mocking\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/client/clientset/versioned/fake` for typed client mocking\n\n---\n\n## Acceptance Criteria\n\n1. ✅ All test files created (cleanup_test.go, batch_test.go, retry_test.go, events_test.go)\n2. ✅ All delta-spec scenarios (AR-038-001-A through AR-038-002-E) implemented\n3. ✅ Unit test pass rate: 100%\n4. ✅ Test coverage ≥ 70%\n5. ✅ Code passes `go vet` and `gofmt`\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Size: L - Large change requiring comprehensive testing across multiple modules\n- Tests should use table-driven test patterns for parameterized scenarios\n- Use fake Kubernetes clientsets to avoid external dependencies\n- Each task is independently verifiable and can be completed in any order within a phase","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/tasks.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-038/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775881471498,"end":1775881471523}}}}
